"title": "7141: people of God, in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7141: people of god, in ot",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The OT relates how God called Israel to be his people.</p>\n<h2>Chosen by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:37\">DEU 4:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:8\">1KI 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:9\">ISA 41:8–41:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1\">ISA 43:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:1-Isa44:2\">ISA 44:1–44:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:5\">EZK 20:5</a></p>\n<h2>Loved by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:37\">DEU 4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:5\">DEU 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:9\">1KI 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:3\">PSA 44:3</a></p>\n<h2>Sanctified by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:9\">DEU 28:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:6\">EXO 19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:31\">EXO 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">DEU 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:12\">ISA 62:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's possession</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">DEU 14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:18\">DEU 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:4\">PSA 135:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1\">ISA 43:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17\">MAL 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's inheritance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:20\">DEU 4:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:26\">DEU 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:29\">DEU 9:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:9\">PSA 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:12\">PSA 33:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:9\">PSA 68:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:2\">PSA 74:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:2\">JOL 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:14\">MIC 7:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:36\">DEU 32:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:6\">NEH 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:14\">PSA 135:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:9\">ISA 41:8–41:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:22\">EXO 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:6\">DEU 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:16\">ISA 63:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:19\">JER 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:9\">JER 31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a></p>\n<h2>God's sheep</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6-Ps95:7\">PSA 95:6–95:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:11–34:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:9\">PSA 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:1\">PSA 74:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:13\">PSA 79:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1\">PSA 80:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:3\">PSA 100:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:11\">ISA 40:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:1\">JER 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:10\">JER 31:10</a></p>",
